metadata.name: Real Imaginary | #1 Shivering Depth
metadata.description:
Discover parallel realities in the Real Imaginary Verse where laws of physics cease to exist and curvature of spacetime becomes infinite.

Collect a piece of time and space where the density of matter grows out of control and causes irreversible outcomes. Real Imaginary Singularities is an edition collection of artifacts living on the Ethereum blockchain from my personal exploration of the nature and behavior of matter and energy. 

Each item has been carefully curated and programmatically generated from a rich set of mathematical and visual attributes to highlight the beauty, diversity and magical correlation to our world. Produced by custom software written for the experiment. 

This collection is the genesis foundation of a tradable and collectable blockchain playable card game to be built and refined by the community owning these tokens.

"Parallel Realities. Here and now. Other vibrations. Other frequencies.” ― Ella Nicolai

Discover more at https://linktr.ee/realimaginary
